# Privacy Policy

Portly collects only the following information from you: target domains/IP addresses and scan results. Portly collects the target domains/IP addresses when you input them into Portly, and Portly collects scan results as a result of you scanning a target domain/IP address. All information is retained within the app on the iOS device that collects it. Portly does not upload this information from your iOS device, nor share it with any other app or third party. Your scan results are only transmitted from your iOS device if and when you chose to do so via the export function and only to the app/service you specify.

Your target domains/IP addresses and scan results are deleted from your device if you delete Portly.

By using Portly, you consent to this Privacy Policy. If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you may email PortlyApp@gmail.com
